{"tid":1632634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【無圖】【民調結果】禁蒙面法？嚇我唔到㗎喎","createTime":"2019-10-06T19:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T10:29:13.000Z","uid":35215,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"46d7726a8fc5ac43d8f1e6b963c13d68e9ca0280","tid":1632634,"uid":35215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:09:24.000Z","msg":"（二樓有收集大家對裝修同拆鐵睇法嘅問卷）<br />\n<br />\n特區政府於十月四日《緊急法》頒布《禁蒙面法》禁止示威者於公眾活動中隱藏臉容。阿叔於宣布當日即時發佈民調，以了解民眾對於禁蒙面法之看法，共取得2,048份有效問卷。<br />\n<br />\n由結果可見，實施禁蒙面法前後參與反修例行動的人數<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">並無明顯下降</span></span></strong>，而大部份的示威者，無論是採用哪一種抗爭手法，均表示會在<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">立法後繼續蒙面</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n在1,786位表示立法後會參與抗爭的受訪者之中，有45.9%表示將會採用和理非之表達手法，38.2%將進行勇武抗爭，15.9%將採用其他抗爭方式。<br />\n<br />\n值得關注的是，設立禁蒙面法後，有超過300名受訪者（即<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">18%表示會繼續參與示威之受訪者</span></strong></span>）將由<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">和由非轉為勇武派</span></span></strong>，反映蒙面法或有反效果。反觀原本為勇武的示威者則無太大立場上的轉變，此法成效備受質疑。<br />\n<br />\n結果如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ceR8g2F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FceR8g2F.png&h=55a42d84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sA2bZf0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsA2bZf0.png&h=2a1e58c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFacebook post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/KongPollster/posts/423199935264652\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FKongPollster%2Fposts%2F423199935264652&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpoCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=0be17787\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/KongPollster/posts/423199935264652</a><br />\n<br />\n上次民意調查發表：<br />\n【要人！】一張圖話你知邊條戰線最缺人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1594905/page/14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1594905/page/14</a>"},{"pid":"e3f4b483834fb1a68317b89a1ac2e0f23362bc3d","tid":1632634,"uid":35215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:09:39.000Z","msg":"睇完禁蒙面法嘅分析，可唔可以幫手share呢個大家對裝修同拆鐵睇法嘅問卷，好短㗎咋<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/EYBzo1MQDJfFNCQV9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FEYBzo1MQDJfFNCQV9&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpoCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=57419313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/EYBzo1MQDJfFNCQV9</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UZqAGxR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUZqAGxR.jpg&h=4df4c264&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f921fbfa078a58e2157707e6fba3b920f60ade9","tid":1632634,"uid":35215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:12:22.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9f723e490cedaf9d473e47c7f9ee3e553cfb2fef","tid":1632634,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:12:58.000Z","msg":"「認真」各位手足 借東風啊！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629930</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n麻煩幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"892f612323ee31a9a8610a3d7cc00dee5786e06f","tid":1632634,"uid":55128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:15:29.000Z","msg":"好ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係政府直接逼人和理非轉勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b255fd2708fe1a580fc9dfb96f9ab34c4d565ac4","tid":1632634,"uid":135517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df34c4e31f7aa02765913207302fe43ad71fce2c","tid":1632634,"uid":135517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06